case.title: Cute Tall Black Female For Dancing Or Body Rubs (Long Island & Queens) - 28 (Midtown)
case.text: Hello! This is not for dating, it's for a service. The other area is not frequented so I am here. I give dancing or body rubs or a combination of both. Fun, tall, medium-light-to-brown skinned Black American female. Not f.u.ll service. Slender to average build and height and weight proportionate, good listener and fun to be around. $50 per half-hour, minimum of 1 hour. Thanks, you can contact to set up a time for this weekend!
